I"è<h1 id="assignments">Assignments</h1>

<h2 id="creating-and-modifying-assignments">Creating and modifying assignments</h2>

<p>On the home page, click on Get Started.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/assignments1_gradus.png" alt="getting started" /></p>

<p>Next click on the Add new assignment button and the following form will show up. Enter in your current progress, set your due date and name your assignment. Then save it!</p>

<p><img src="/assets/assignments2_gradus.png" alt="new assignment" /></p>

<p>It will show up on the table and you can then click Options to modify the progress.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/assignments3_gradus.png" alt="change assignment" /></p>

<p>If you want to mark it as done, hover over the checkmark and click it to finish the assignment.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/assignments4_gradus.png" alt="marking as done" /></p>

<h2 id="viewing-assignments-and-progress">Viewing assignments and progress</h2>

<p>On the home page, the most recently added assignments will be displayed in a row of 3. There is a progress bar, and if you are finished, click Mark as done.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/assignments5_gradus.png" alt="home page" /></p>
